Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=19}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.55,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Saul!{Enies 09 - 30:49}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:53.89,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:58.47,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Making an enemy of me\Nwill be the last thing you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's Vice Admiral Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,First he escapes with Olvia,\Nand now he's attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,W-We don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The island is finished! - OG}The island's done for!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It'll all burn to rubble! - OG}It'll all burn to ash!{Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't give up! Save the books!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have to preserve this history! - OG}History must be told!{Z/Rin - Lit. "Tell history!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Throw them into the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:39.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's better than having them burn up! Quickly! - OG}It's better than letting them burn up! Hurry!{rangicus/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:51.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saul! Stop it already! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Throw the books out of the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Save as many books as possible! - OG}Save as many as possible!{Z- "books" was just in the previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Preserve as many pages as we can! - OG}Preserve as many pages as you can!{AR}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:03.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(266,568)}{So that our ancestors' words... - OG}So that thousands of years\Nof our ancestors' words...{PP- also the lit. TL}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(566,0)}...will reach the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:11.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Run to the evacuation ship while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You won't survive if you stay here! - OG}You won't survive if you stay on this island!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Mother! - OG}Mom!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shoot Saul! - OG}Fire at Saul!{Z - "Shoot Saul" works fine, but it almost reads like he could be telling Saul to do the shooting.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:03.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Robin! Hurry and run! - OG}Robin! Hurry up and run!{WF/rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What was your mother's last wish?! - OG}Remember your mother's last wish!{WF/rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.61,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,230,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)\fad(0,2028)}Live, Robin!{Enies 09 - 27:10}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The evacuation ship is departing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wait! There's someone coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Go away, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Well... wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:30.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Isn't she the daughter of that criminal,\NOlvia, who was in the paper earlier? - OG}Isn't she the daughter of Olvia,\Nthat criminal who was in the paper?{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:35.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! If we let her on the ship,\Nit might cause us trouble! - OG}That's right! If we let her on the ship,\Nit might cause us trouble too!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be ridiculous! She's only a child!\NHurry and get her on the ship! - OG}{That's just far fetched! She's only a child!\NHurry and bring her aboard! - Z: new line to bring the CPS down}That's ridiculous! She's just a kid!\NHurry and bring her aboard!{Panda/Kris - further tweaked}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evacuation ship, do not let that brat on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,She may be a child,\Nbut she's also an archaeologist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She is a target of our operation! - OG}She's one of this operation's targets!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chief Spandine! I-Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,See? If we {\i1}had{\i0} let her\Non board, we'd be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:55.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That must be CP9! Those worthless scum! - OG}{CP9...! Of all the worthless\Nthings you could do...! - Z/PP}CP9?! Of all the useless...!{PP/PJ/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chief! Vice Admiral Saul is coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:06.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Really?! I guess we didn't\Nhave to ask Olvia about his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire the cannons at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ice Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Partisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kuzan-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}It's Kuzan!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, my, my. - OG}Well, well, well...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:38.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It wouldn't look good if a deserter\Nprevented a buster call, would it? - OG}It'd be a bad look if a deserter\Nobstructed a buster call, y'know?{Z/Kris/Panda/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:43.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is this really honorable? - OG}Are you proud of what's happening here?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This isn't right!\NYou should know that! - OG}This ain't right! You damn well know that!{Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a warning! - OG}To set an example...!{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:53.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ohara is being wiped out to make an example! - OG}Ohara is being annihilated to set an example!{Z/WF/rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:57.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If it benefits the future of the world, it can't be helped. - OG}If it benefits the future\Nof the world, then so be it!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:06:00.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,In fact, these scholars\Nhave broken the law, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:04.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Justice has a different meaning depending on your position. - OG}Depending on your point of view,\Njustice can take on a whole new meaning.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So I won't criticize yours. - OG}So I won't criticize your version of it.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:10.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But if you're going to get in our way- OG}{Even so, getting in our way... - Z}However, if you're thinking\Nof getting in our way...{Kris/Panda/rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't let you do that. - OG}{is out of the question. - Z}I can't ignore it.{Kris/Panda/rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The evacuation ship was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was cannon fire! From one of the battleships! - OG}A battleship... fired on it!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It came from Vice Admiral Sakazuki's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we are going to do this,\Nwe must do it thoroughly. - OG}We must be thorough in our endeavors.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If even a single scholar were to be hiding on that ship... - OG}If even a single scholar\Nwas hiding on that ship...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the sacrifices we've made here would be in vain. - OG}our sacrifices here would have been in vain.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We must eradicate even\Nthe smallest possibility of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:48.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is this really justice?! - OG}You call this justice?!{Z/Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you still claim to be in the right?! - OG}Can you still claim the moral high ground?!{Z/Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I never intended to go as far as that idiot! - OG}Don't lump me in with that moron!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're getting out of here, Robin! - OG}We're making a run for it, Robin!{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's abnormally strong! - OG}His strength is out of this world!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saul ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He's taking a scholar with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ice Time Capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saul! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:18.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Run with all your might!{Used as flashback in Enies Lobby 22 @10:20}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You'll die if you stay on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sail out on my raft! - OG}Sail out to sea on my raft!{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And you, Saul? - OG}What about you, Saul?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is it for me. He got me. - OG}I'm done for. He got me good.{Z/Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to! I'd be alone at sea! - OG}No! I don't want to be alone at sea!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're alone now, but you're\Nsure to meet friends someday! - OG}Although you're alone now,{Panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:47.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're alone now, but you're\Nsure to meet friends someday! - OG}you're sure to meet some friends someday!{Panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The sea is vast, so someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:01.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,you'll find friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:05.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No one is born into this world to be alone! - OG}No one is {\i1}ever{\i0} born\Ninto this world completely alone!{Rin/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Run, Robin! Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:16.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When you're having a bad day,\Nlaugh like this, just like I taught you! - OG}When the pain gets to be too much,\Nlaugh like this, just like I taught you!{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ice Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:31.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go meet the friends who are waiting\Nfor you somewhere out there, Robin! - OG}Somewhere in the vast sea\Nyou'll find true friends.{Z/Rin}{11:22}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go meet the friends who are waiting\Nfor you somewhere out there, Robin! - OG}They're out there waiting for you, Robin!{Z/Rin}{11:22}{08:28/08:31}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:42.13,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1527)}{Live together with them. - OG}True friends you can live a real life with...!{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:59.89,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{So, this is the history humans have chosen. - OG}So, this is the history humanity has chosen.{Kris/rangicus/Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:03.27,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{How thoughtless our race is... - OG}How thoughtless we can be...{Z/Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.78,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.61,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.91,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{any parting words as a mother. - OG}any parting words as your mother.{Kris/rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Knowledge... has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:32.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Absolute justice sometimes\Ndrives people mad. - OG}The idea of absolute justice\Nhas been known to drive people mad.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:35.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I've decided to let you\Nescape from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:39.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What could possibly sprout\Nfrom the seed Saul tended? - OG}I wonder what could sprout\Nfrom the seed Saul tended to?{Kris/Panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whom you bear a grudge against is up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:46.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,but for now, just be happy you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Live as quietly as possible. - OG}{Don't make any waves out there. - Z}Try to keep a low profile.{panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I laid a track of ice on the sea. - OG}I've laid a track of ice on the sea.{panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:56.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If you just go straight\Nin that small boat, you'll reach land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Now, remember this:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm not your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:07.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm your enemy. I'll be the first\Nto come after you if you cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My mother is on the island! - OG}My mom is on the island!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No one will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If that pain makes you wish for death,\Nyou're free to take that path as well. - OG}{If the pain is too much to bear,\Ndeath is also an option. - Z - maybe we can soften the suggestive suicide language}If the pain is too much to bear...\Nthe choice is yours.{Poppy}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.89,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the best library in the world. - OG}This is the greatest library in the world.{Rin}{Enies 08 - 29:00 (kinda)}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.39,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Do you like books?{Enies 08 - 29:10}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.15,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,234,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}Today is Robin's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:28.27,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,268,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}– Happy birthday, Robin!\N– Happy birthday, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.94,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,183,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}Hold your head high, Robin!{Enies 09 - 27:47}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.86,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ohara is honorable!{Enies 09 - 27:51}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:37.41,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,232,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}We cannot forsake\Nthe future of your generation!{Enies 09 - 26:32}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.45,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,229,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}So laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.79,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,When the pain gets\Nto be too much, just laugh.{Enies 08 - 19:43; Also a near repeat of the line in this episode at 08:12}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.71,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2107,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}It seems dumb to laugh\Nwhen you're in pain.{Enies 08 - 19:46}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.88,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,That's not true.{Enies 08 - 19:48}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:28.29,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Somewhere in the vast sea you'll find true friends.\NThey're out there waiting for you, Robin!{08:28/08:31}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That'd be impossible. - OG}Not a chance.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:49.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Th-This is... - OG}Th-The lake...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There are enough books\Nto completely fill the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Was this by chance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is the brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where'd you find her?! Did you capture her? - OG}Where was she?! Did you catch her?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, sir! We were looking for a suspicious girl, as ordered... - OG}{No, sir! Our orders were\Nto find a suspicious girl, - Z}No, sir! We followed a lead\Nabout a suspicious girl{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and found this girl on a passenger ship leaving an island...\Nfar to the northeast of Ohara, - OG}{and while we saw this one leaving an island on\Na passenger ship far northeast of Ohara, - Z}and managed to find her on a passenger ship\Nleaving an island far northeast of Ohara,{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but we lost her right after that. - OG}but we soon lost sight of her.{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,She's got the devil's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:33.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I definitely saw a brat escaping\Nfrom the burning Ohara on a small boat! - OG}{\q2}Back then, when Ohara was engulfed in flames,\NI did see a brat escaping on a small boat!{Z/Kris/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:39.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to go after her, but the helm\Nsuddenly got stuck as if it was frozen! - OG}But before I could chase after her,\Nthe helm got stuck like it was frozen in place.{Z/Panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I bet Saul let her escape right before he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If she can decipher the poneglyphs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,she's dangerous regardless of her youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:55.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This operation will come to nothing unless we capture her as soon as possible—I don't care how! - OG}{[/q2]I don't care how you do it; capture her immediately,\Nor else this operation will amount to nothing! - Z}{\q2}Use all available means toward her immediate capture,\Nor else this operation will amount to nothing!{Z/Panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seventy-nine million berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Such a high bounty\Nfor an eight-year-old girl?! - OG}A bounty that high for an eight-year-old girl?!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:10.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They said that she's a survivor of those Ohara devils who planned the destruction of the world. - OG}They say she's a survivor of those Ohara devils\Nwho were plotting the world's destruction.{Z/Kris/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:17.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know how, but they said\Nthat she sank six Marine battleships. - OG}I don't know how, but they say\Nthat she sank six Marine battleships.{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So that's why her bounty is so high. - OG}That explains the high bounty.{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard the government and Marine HQ are directly involved in the search. - OG}I heard the government and\NMarine HQ themselves are hunting her.{Z/WF - this is one of those rare moments where I'll bring headquarters down to "HQ." It should be fine every once in a while because people really do say this in normal speech, and it will help CPS here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:27.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seems like she inherited the ideology\Nof the executed scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It'll be a problem if she's left at large. - OG}She can't be left at large.{Z/Panda}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:33.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,She's a devil's spawn\Nwho shouldn't be left alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sure. - OG}Oh, no.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thank you for letting me work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:44.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By the way, before lunch\Nyou have guests. - OG}By the way, before we eat lunch,\Nthere are some guests here to see you.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, give me the money!\NI gave her up, didn't I?! - OG}Now, pay up! I'm the one who\Ngave you the tip, after all!{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,She's small, but she works very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh? You're still up? - OG}Oh? You're still awake?{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:01.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We have to go shopping in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get some rest. - OG}Get some rest soon.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's a good kid, but if we're with her,\Nwe'll be in danger too. - OG}She's a good kid, but letting her\Nstay here puts us at risk too.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Besides, look at this bounty! - OG}And besides, look at this bounty!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:14.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Honey! She isn't in her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! That little brat caught on! - OG}Dammit! The little brat caught on!{Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, but I don't have any food. - OG}I'm sorry. I don't have any food.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I know about you, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm a wanted man, too. - OG}I'm a wanted man myself.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:41.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you do chores, I'll feed you. - OG}If you help out around here, you get fed.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Captain!\N– Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Contact Marine Headquarters! - OG}Marine Headquarters...!{PP/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:50.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where's Robin?! Hand her over, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That damn jinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:57.17,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(516,0)}Your sin is being alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.84,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(519,0)}What?! Nico Robin is in town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:04.80,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1022)}Find her! Hand her over to the government!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A poneglyph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:15.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,483)}{Don't come here! I've got nothing to sell you! - OG}Stay away from my shop!\NI've got nothing to sell you!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm sixteen. I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Please let me join your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.19,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,You betrayed me, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want you to help me. - OG}I'm in need of your assistance.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:33.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1068)}I heard that you can read poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:41.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If... you exercise a buster call\Nright here, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{then together with Enies Lobby... - OG}then not only Enies Lobby...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:50.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you will also meet your demise. - OG}but every single one of you will be obliterated!{Z/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{D-Don't be ridiculous! - OG}Th-That's the stupidest...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way our allies would target us! - OG}Our allies know better than to target us!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you saying?! - OG}Just what are you trying to say?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:01.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Twenty years ago,\Neverything was taken away from me... - OG}Twenty years ago,\Nthey took everything from me...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and many people's lives were ruined. - OG}{and countless lives were ruined. - Rin}and devastated so many lives...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was caused by a single attack - OG}with just one attack—{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a buster call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That attack is now... - OG}And now that attack...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:16.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is aimed at the friends I found\Nwho let me lower my guard. - OG}is being directed at the friends\Nwho finally allowed me to lower my guard.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:23.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The more I wish to be with you,\Nthe more my fate will threaten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:29.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter how far I travel at sea,\NI face a colossal enemy that I can't avoid... - OG}No matter how far I travel at sea,\NI face a colossal enemy that I can't outrun...{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:34.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy! - OG}{because the world and its darkness\Nare my enemies! - Z}because my enemy is the world itself,\Nas well as all the darkness therein.{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:37.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The incident with Aokiji, and this... - OG}There was the run-in\Nwith Aokiji, and now this...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've already dragged you\Ninto my troubles twice! - OG}My troubles have hurt you twice!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:45.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If this continues forever,\Nno matter how good-natured you are... - OG}If this continues forever,\Nno matter your best intentions,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you'll eventually feel that I'm a burden! - OG}you'll eventually see me as a burden!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:52.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{One day, I'm sure you'll betray and abandon me! - OG}Then one day, you'll inevitably\Nbetray and abandon me!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm most afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:58.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want you\Nto come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I'm going to die someday anyway, - OG}If I'm as good as dead,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want to die right here, right now! - OG}then I choose to die right here, right now!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin{-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now it makes sense. - OG}It all makes sense now.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see! That indeed\Nis a sound argument! - OG}I see! That is indeed a sound argument!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:27.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I mean, no one is stupid enough\Nto think it's better with you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Look at that symbol, you damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:42.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{That logo symbolizes the\Nunity of over 170 countries spanning the four blues and the Grand Line. - OG}Its mark symbolizes the unity of over 170 countries,\Nspanning the four blues and the Grand Line.{Z/Kris}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you now understand\Nhow completely powerless your opposition is?! - OG}Does that hammer home how utterly\Ninsignificant you are against all that?!{Rin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:56.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you realize how huge the organization chasing this woman is?! - OG}Do you understand the sheer size\Nof the organization chasing this woman?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know Robin's enemy now. - OG}{I understand who Robin's enemy is. - Z}I know who Robin's enemy is now.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shoot down that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This is my new weapon,\Na huge slingshot I call Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Take a good look at its power! - OG}Marvel at its power!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:18.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:27.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Th-They've gone and done it! - OG}N-Now they've done it!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:42.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do they understand\Nwhat it means to attack that flag?! - OG}Do they understand\Nwhat it means to attack a flag?!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:48.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The pirates declared war\Nagainst the World Government! - OG}Those pirates just declared war\Non the World Government!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you insane?! -OG}Are you all insane?!{Z}{Used as flashback for Enies Lobby 23 @timestamp 31:53}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:53.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't think that you'll be able to survive after making the entire world your enemy! - OG}{Making the entire world your enemy\Nmeans you're all as good as dead! - Z/PJ}You're all as good as dead after\Nmaking the world your enemy!{AR}{Used as flashback for Enies Lobby 11 @01:52}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:58.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!{OG}{That's fine by me! - PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:09.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:14.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We still haven't heard you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Say you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:26.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.07,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,To live...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:40.70,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\t(0,229,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&)}You shouldn't be allowed\Nto live in this world, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:44.91,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\t(0,230,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&)}Your existence itself is a huge crime, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.92,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought it was something I dared not wish for. - OG}This is something I dared not wish for.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.84,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,No one ever {\i1}let{\i0} me wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.51,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,I want to die!{Enies 07 - 16:44 (without the "もう")}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:03.10,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,231,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}The sea is vast, so someday...{07:53}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:06.94,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,you'll find friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.40,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,480,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)\t(2273,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Believe in Luffy.{W7 20 - 29:14}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.41,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.37,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,it's really okay for me\Nto utter my wish just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.37,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1148)}I want to live!{Wano 58 - 02:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:36.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,985)}Take me back to sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:03.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You guys...! I love you guys, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
